snippet.title: Halloween - Official Announcement Trailer | gamescom2025
snippet.description:
Michael Myers Returns to Haddonfield. Check out the Halloween trailer for the upcoming asymmetric stealth horror game with single and multiplayer modes from developer and publisher IllFonic, co-published by Gun Interactive, and in partnership with Compass International Pictures and Further Front. Halloween will be available on Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5 (PS5), and PC via Steam and Epic Game Store in 2026.

Step into the chilling world of John Carpenter‚Äôs genre-defining film, now transformed into a suspenseful one-versus-many stealth horror experience in Halloween. Put on the iconic mask to become the ultimate slasher, Michael Myers, stalking and executing the citizens of Haddonfield one by one, or striving to thwart Michael Myers‚Äô plans as Civilians determined to save the unaware townsfolk before it‚Äôs too late. 

Stick to the shadows as Civilians, seeking out Haddonfield residents to warn them and searching for a way to contact the authorities. As Michael Myers, give them a reason to fear the dark and cut the phone lines to prevent the police from ruining his favorite holiday.

#IGN #Gaming #gamescom2025

snippet.title: Season 18: Stadium Quick Play Official Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Bigger battles and bolder strategies await in Season 18: Stadium Quick Play!

Stadium Quick Play is here with shorter match times, quicker Item economy, backfill support, and Cross Play! Dominate as Winston, Brigitte, and Pharah at season launch, and shake things up with Tracer when she arrives in Stadium during Mid-season.

We‚Äôre also bringing a brand new game mode to Stadium with Payload Race, 3 new maps, and the new Draft Mode which gives players a pre-match advantage, enabling smart counter-picks and better team coordination.

Make a splash with Wuyang, the prodigy from Wuxing University and our newest Support Hero. With a skillset built for tactical repositioning and team utility, Wuyang rewards players who thrive on timing, precision, and adaptability.

Over 50 new Perks are arriving at launch, with each Hero getting at least one new one! In addition to new Perks, Season 18 is also bringing a Competitive Rank Reset, allowing a fresh start for everyone.

And we‚Äôve only just starched the surface! Look out for Sojourn‚Äôs brand-new Ultraviolet Sentinel Mythic Skin, the new Season 18 Premium Battle Pass, and so much more!

Bring your A-game to the arena when Season 18: Stadium Quick Play launches on Aug 26.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_
Follow #Overwatch2 for the latest news:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playoverwatch
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@overwatch
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playoverwatch

snippet.title: Sister Wives New Season Trailer | TLC
snippet.description:
The Browns are back and more emotionally raw than ever. In the wake of multiple separations, the family faces major turning points. Meri dips her toe into dating with an awkward but promising speed dating event, while Janelle takes steps toward a spiritual divorce after a freeing trip to New Orleans. Christine and David are settling into married life, but Christine is shaken when her kids begin moving to North Carolina near Janelle, sparking jealousy and hurt. 

Sister Wives returns Sunday, September 28 at 10pm ET/PT.

Stranger Things 5 
The fifth and final season of the American science fiction horror drama television series Stranger Things, marketed as Stranger Things 5, will be released on the streaming service Netflix. The season will be produced by the show's creators, the Duffer brothers, along with Shawn Levy and Dan Cohen.
A fifth season of "Stranger Things" is expected in 2025. Actor David Harbour told GQ that he expects filming to begin in 2023 for the fifth season of "Very Stranger Things," and that it will premiere in mid-2024.

Stranger Things is an American science fiction horror drama television series created by the Duffer Brothers for Netflix. Produced by Monkey Massacre Productions and 21 Laps Entertainment, the first season was released on Netflix on July 15, 2016. The second and third season followed in October 2017 and July 2019 respectively, and the fourth season aired in two parts in May and July 2022. In February 2022, Stranger Things was renewed for a fifth and final season.
Set in the 1980s, the series centers around the residents of the fictional small town of Hawkins, Indiana, as they are plagued by a hostile alternate dimension known as the Upside Down, after a nearby human experimentation facility opens a gateway between it and the normal world. The ensemble cast includes Winona Ryder, David Harbour, Finn Wolfhard, Millie Bobby Brown, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Matthew Modine, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Joe Keery, Dacre Montgomery, Sean Astin, Paul Reiser, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson and Brett Gelman. Stranger Things trailer concept, Stranger Things Season 5, Stranger Things Season 5 trailer,  The Duffer Brothers developed Stranger Things as a mix of investigative drama and supernatural elements portrayed with horror and childlike sensibilities, while infusing references to the pop culture of the 1980s. Several thematic and directorial elements were inspired by the works of Steven Spielberg, John Carpenter, David Lynch, Stephen King, Wes Craven and H. P. Lovecraft. They also took inspiration from experiments conducted during the Cold War and conspiracy theories involving secret government programs.
One of Netflix's flagship series, Stranger Things has attracted record viewership on the streaming platform. Stranger Things Season 5 teaser trailer.It has been critically acclaimed for its characterization, atmosphere, acting, soundtrack, directing, writing, and homages to 1980s films. It has received numerous nominations and awards. An animated spin-off series, developed by Eric Robles and produced by Flying Bark Productions, is in development.

snippet.title: Zach Top - South Of Sanity
snippet.description:
The official visualizer for Zach Top's single "South Of Sanity" from the highly anticipated album Ain't In It For My Health. Available now: https://leo33.lnk.to/southofsanityyt

Ain't In It For My Health: https://leo33.lnk.to/aintinitformyhealthyt

Lyrics:
Playin' a rodeo in Montana tonight
She's two thousand miles away
Says she loves me on the phone as she cries
Wishes I‚Äôd come home to stay
 
But I‚Äôm somewhere outside of Missoula 
They just called my name from the stage
When we hung up she was talkin' leavin'
Now how am I supposed to sing and play
She's left me somewhere south of sanity 
Still just north of insane
 
The show is over I tried twice to call her back
But no answer either time
My thoughts are racin' like a fast car 'round the track
Aw and I can't get her off my mind
 
And I'm somewhere outside Albuquerque
They just called my name from the stage
When we last talked she was talkin' leavin'
Now how am I supposed to sing and play
She's left me somewhere south of sanity 
Still just north of 
 
Startin' to believe I might be losin' everything
 
Still I‚Äôm somewhere outside Amarillo
They just called my name from the stage
When we last talked she was talkin' leavin'
But I gotta show I gotta play
Somewhere south of sanity 
Still just north of insane

Written by Zach Top, Carson Chamberlain and Mark Nesler

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

There are two folks that keep the town of Dry Dock safe: Shadow and Sonic. Yep. The Black and Blue ain‚Äôt playing out any Sonic vs Shadow story this time. Well‚Ä¶ they trying not to, at least. Shadow the Hedgehog needs to work with his nemesis if the townsfolk have any chance of surviving this land of magical six-shooters. Traveling in a fried-out Kombi
On a hippie trail, head full of zombie
I met a strange lady, she made me nervous
She took me in and gave me breakfast
And she said

"Do you come from a land down under?
Where women glow and men plunder
Can't you hear, can't you hear the thunder?
You better run, you better take cover"

Buyin' bread from a man in Brussels
He was six-foot-four and full of muscle

You better run, you better take cover", yeah

snippet.title: OBLIVION REMASTERED IS A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME ‚Ñ¢ - Infinite Stats Is 100% Developer Approved  üÑÆ
snippet.description:
Well Oblivion Remastered is now Here and I have been playing it endlessly discovering new and classical exploits to create some truly absurdly broken bugs and glitches. On this quest we are joined by our hero reanu keeves, the most breath taking individual in gaming. And I mean it because his stats are so broken that he can suck the air out of your lungs. So this should be easy. However the Developers and bethesda did have the time to patch out and remove some of This Elder Scrolls most famous exploits, bugs and glitches. The Oblivion Item Duplication with scrolls is gone, Dorian Infinite Gold Glitch Gone and many more have been taken in the name of making a more perfectly balanced video game experience. 

I Am The Spiffing brit and my goal today is to see if this is in fact a perfectly balanced game with no exploits or if perhaps the developers over at Virtuos have in fact added in brand new perfectly overpowered bugs and glitches for someone like myself to use to break the game! So today we summon our greatest skyrim hero into the world with the creation of Oblivion Reanu Keeves the single most powerful video game entity ever created.

[Intro: Pharrell Williams]
Hey

He didn't walk up with that "how you doin'?" (Uh)
When he came in the room
He said there's a lot of girls I can do with (Uh)
But I can't without you
I knew him forever in a minute (Hey)
That summer night in June
And papa says he got malo in him (Uh)

[Pre-Chorus: Camila Cabello & Pharrell Williams]
He got me feelin' like, "Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh" (Ayy)
I knew it when I met him (Ayy), I loved him when I left him

Oh, na-na-na-na-na (Woo)


[Chorus: Camila Cabello & Pharrell Williams]
Havana, ooh, na-na (Hey, hey)
Half of my heart is in Havana, ooh na-na (Hey, hey, uh-huh)

Havana, ooh, na-na

[Verse 2: Young Thug]
(Jeffery) Just graduated, fresh on campus, hm
Fresh out East Atlanta with no manners, damn
Fresh out East Atlanta
(Bump, bump) Bump on her bumper like a traffic jam

Back it on me (Back it up)
Shawty cravin' on me, get to eatin' on me (On me)
She waited on me (And what?)
Shawty cakin' on me, got the bacon on me (Wait up)
This is history in the makin', homie (Homie)
Point blank, close range, that B (Tah, tah)
If it cost a million, that's me (That's me)
I was gettin' mula, baby

[Chorus: Camila Cabello & Pharrell Williams]
Havana, ooh, na-na (Hey, hey)
Half of my heart is in Havana, ooh, na-na (Hey, hey; oh, oh)
He took me back to East Atlanta (Uh-huh), na-na-na (Oh no)
Oh, but my heart is in Havana (Huh)
My heart is in Havana (Ayy)
Havana, ooh, na-na
[Bridge: Starrah, Camila Cabello, Both]
Ooh, na-na, oh, na-na-na (Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh)
Take me back, back, back, like (Yeah, babe)
Ooh, na-na, oh, na-na-na
Take me back, back, back, like (Yeah, yeah)
Ooh, na-na, oh, na-na-na
Take me back, back, back like (Yeah, babe)
Ooh, na-na, oh, na-na-na
Take me back, back, back (Ah)
Ayy, ayy
Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh (Ayy)
Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh (Ayy)
Take me back to my Havana

[Chorus: Camila Cabello & Pharrell Williams]
Havana, ooh, na-na
Half of my heart is in Havana, ooh, na-na (Oh, yeah)
He took me back to East Atlanta, na-na-na (Hey, hey)
Oh, but my heart is in Havana
My heart is in Havana (Hey)
Havana, ooh, na-na (Uh-huh)

[Outro: Starrah & Camila Cabello]
Oh, na-na-na (Oh, na, yeah)
Oh, na-na-na
Oh, na-na-na (No, no, no, take me back)
Oh, na-na-na
Havana, ooh, na-na

Every shadow asksing me to come.

Where I‚Äôll be buried when I go.

No one comes, no help appears.

Through ninety-nine nights of endless night.

Some kids vanish, some kids stay,
Some kids laugh ‚Äòcause they‚Äôve gone insane.
Whispers in the dark, pulling at my sleeve,
Telling me lies I almost believe.

The deer‚Äôs not the only thing out here‚Äî
There‚Äôs voices, claws and things unclear.

Some nights eat your only friend.

With new kids trapped where I have been.

snippet.title: d
snippet.description:
Absolute domination (by me AND my opponents!) Get wrecked Mika

Competitive Mario Kart has its own rating system (called MMR, or Matchmaking Rating), which is a number that determines your skill. Unlike online worldwides, we can pick any regular track, and intermissions are not allowed!

How to do all the best shortcuts: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XFJmt_LEUa0
How to play regular tracks online: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLIt4s7NKM0

How to join competitive:
- https://lounge.mkcentral.com/mkworld
- Click on the Discord invite link at the top
- Read the rules and follow the instructions
- You can ask questions in the Discord!

snippet.title: This Needs To STOP.. (Schlep Vs. Roblox)
snippet.description:
The Schlep vs Roblox drama hit a new low with Roblox YouTuber PMDamiann EXPOSED? 

So last week Roblox YouTuber Schlep known for his Pred Catching series on Roblox 'To Catch a Robloxian', where he collaborates with Ruben Sim, Jidion and more, was BANNED off of Roblox and THREATENED with a Lawsuit after Schlep received a CEASE AND DESIST from the Roblox Corporation. The Roblox Schlep Lawsuit / Ban Drama has gone VIRAL with many Large YouTuber's covering the Schlep Roblox Moderation Situation such as Charlie / MoistCritical, KreekCraft, Ruben Sim, Jidion and others. Roblox is now THREATENING to BAN other Roblox YouTubers including myself with their new HORRIBLE roblox moderation policies which Schlep had called them out for before.  RESPONDED by doubling down on their original claims and still refuse to UNBAN SCHLEP or FREE SCHLEP. Roblox Has also released a 40 minute long response video which I has attacked and exposed schlep. Since then another situation has unfolded in relation to the schlep situation where roblox animation youtuber PMDamiann got exposed and attacked because he made an animation about Schlep Sued. Following PMDamiann Exposed, there was another incident when someone known as blockboy192 got doxxed and was unfortunatly forced off the internet due to his saftey. In this video I go over everything so be sure to watch until the end!

Make sure to Leave a LIKE and SUBSCRIBE to help as many people as possible be made aware and informed/educated on this situation! Please watch this video to the end to be informed on the entire drama/situation!

snippet.title: Playing My FAVORITE Slot Machines!
snippet.description:
We are BACK playing ALL of my favorite slots‚Ä¶ and if you‚Äôve been watching the channel for a while, I want you to guess which ones they are! ÔøºThank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you‚Äôre roasting me‚ÄîI still love you. You‚Äôre all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I‚Äôll see you in the next one! Let‚Äôs go to war.
empty.

If you want to play slots and table games, absolutely free and over 40 states click this link below and play on spin quest today. Or tune into a live stream. I'm live on spin quest most weekdays! https://spinquest.com/?u=brettski

Brettski strolled into the casino with swagger in his step and fire in his gut. Dressed in his signature leather jacket and mirrored sunglasses‚Äîindoors, naturally‚Äîhe wasn‚Äôt here to *try* his luck. He was here to *bend* it.

The high-limit room welcomed him like an old friend: cool air, soft jazz, and the hum of machines that could change lives with a flicker of lights. His first stop was *Blazing Phoenix Deluxe*, the slot that once paid him \$24,000 on a random Tuesday. He fed the machine a crisp \$500 bill, pressed Max Bet, and watched the reels spin like the wheels of fate.

Bam‚Äîbonus round. But it fizzled. \$1,200 return. Not bad, but not *Brettski*. He moved on to *Gold Scarab Xtreme*, his secret weapon. Two spins in‚Äî*jackpot tease*. His heart thudded. Then, silence. The machine glitched. Frozen. He flagged an attendant.

‚ÄúSystem reboot,‚Äù they said. ‚ÄúUnusual error.‚Äù

Unusual? Brettski never believed in coincidences. As he waited, a woman in a red dress brushed past him, slipped a folded note into his palm without a word, and vanished into the rows of machines.

He unfolded it.

**"You're being watched. Walk away now if you want to keep winning."**

His spine tingled. Who *was* she? Casino security? A rival gambler? A ghost?

He ignored the warning.

Next up: *Dragon's Fury Platinum*. His ultimate go-to. He sat down, inserted his high-roller card, loaded \$2,000, and hit Max Bet. The screen lit up like fireworks. Three dragons. A gong. Bonus triggered. The progressive jackpot started to climb‚Äî\$100K, \$250K, \$500K...

Then everything went black. The screen, the room, *everything*.

When the lights returned, Brettski was alone.

No machine.

No jackpot.

Just the red dress, draped over his chair.

**To be continued...**



#slots #blackjack #gambling #casino #baccarat #roulette

Who is Brettski? Brettski is a Professional Gambler, similar to the ancient legends Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, Mr. Hand Pay, or Lady Luck HQ! However, unlike these legends, Brettski has thousands of years of stored ancient knowledge harvested by the elders, at skills such as Slot Machines, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, and Baccarat.  Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

Join my Discord Here: https://discord.com/invite/eYeaS2R2JR

Roblox is an online platform and game creation system where users can play games, socialize, and create their own games. It provides a user-friendly environment for developers to design games using the Roblox Studio, a powerful game development tool that employs the Lua programming language for scripting. Games on Roblox are hosted on the platform and can range across various genres, including adventure, role-playing, simulations, racing, and more.

Roblox is available on a variety of platforms, making it accessible to a wide audience. It can be played on Windows and macOS through the dedicated desktop apps, as well as on iPhones and iPads via the Roblox app in the App Store. Android users can access it through the Google Play Store, and Xbox One users can enjoy the platform through a dedicated app available in the Microsoft Store. Additionally, the Roblox website allows for account management, game browsing, and launching games.
